<Link id="l00625" /><CodeLine lineNumber="625"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Thumb BL and BLX use a strange offset encoding where bits 22 and 21 are</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00626" /><CodeLine lineNumber="626"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// determined by negating them and XOR&#39;ing them with bit 23</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00627" /><CodeLine lineNumber="627" lineLink="#ab947196869d4c2d094c9bb9e5ad71800"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">static</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> int32&#95;t <a href="#ab947196869d4c2d094c9bb9e5ad71800">encodeThumbBLOffset</a>(int32&#95;t offset) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00628" /><CodeLine lineNumber="628"><Highlight kind="normal">  offset &gt;&gt;= 1;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00629" /><CodeLine lineNumber="629"><Highlight kind="normal">  uint32&#95;t S  = (offset &amp; 0x800000) &gt;&gt; 23;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00630" /><CodeLine lineNumber="630"><Highlight kind="normal">  uint32&#95;t J1 = (offset &amp; 0x400000) &gt;&gt; 22;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00631" /><CodeLine lineNumber="631"><Highlight kind="normal">  uint32&#95;t J2 = (offset &amp; 0x200000) &gt;&gt; 21;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00632" /><CodeLine lineNumber="632"><Highlight kind="normal">  J1 = (~J1 &amp; 0x1);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00633" /><CodeLine lineNumber="633"><Highlight kind="normal">  J2 = (~J2 &amp; 0x1);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00634" /><CodeLine lineNumber="634"><Highlight kind="normal">  J1 ^= S;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00635" /><CodeLine lineNumber="635"><Highlight kind="normal">  J2 ^= S;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00636" /><CodeLine lineNumber="636"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00637" /><CodeLine lineNumber="637"><Highlight kind="normal">  offset &amp;= ~0x600000;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00638" /><CodeLine lineNumber="638"><Highlight kind="normal">  offset |= J1 &lt;&lt; 22;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00639" /><CodeLine lineNumber="639"><Highlight kind="normal">  offset |= J2 &lt;&lt; 21;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00640" /><CodeLine lineNumber="640"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00641" /><CodeLine lineNumber="641"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">return</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> offset;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00642" /><CodeLine lineNumber="642"><Highlight kind="normal">&#125;</Highlight></CodeLine>
